-- Deutsche Bank Hires Eight to Strengthen Its Listed-Derivatives Business
-- B y   A a r o n   K i r c h f e l d
-- 2010-10-07T13:40:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-07/deutsche-bank-hires-eight-to-strengthen-its-listed-derivatives-business.html
Deutsche Bank AG said it hired eight
people to strengthen its listed-derivatives business.  The new business will be run by Drew Bradford, who will
report to Jon Hitchon, co-head of global prime finance,
according to an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Aaron Kirchfeld at 
 akirchfeld@bloomberg.net  